---
title: Scrambled Eggs
servings: 2
prep time: 2 minutes
cook time: 5 minutes
---

Crack @eggs{3} into a #bowl{}.

Add @milk{2%tbsp} and @salt{1%pinch}.

Whisk until well combined.

Heat @butter{1%tbsp} in a #non-stick pan{} over medium-low heat.

Pour in egg mixture and cook for ~{2%minutes}, stirring gently.

Continue stirring until eggs are just set, about ~{1%minute} more.

Season with @black pepper{} to taste and serve immediately.
